D tisselbi!
Heyyan-asen-d kulci.
Maca yella axir n waya.
Aql-aɣ newweḍ ɣer ṣṣeḥ.
Amezruy-nsen, d ayla-nneɣ.
Yekfa usdewdew-nni n tazwara!
D amdan amellal i t-id-yennan.
Wid yeṛwan, ɛyan ula deg tawant-nsen.
Allal i nessexdem yefḍeḥ mliḥ.
Miksiku, hudden-tt, ulac acu ǧǧan deg-s.
Ur ngiren ara ɣef yiwen n ubrid, d tirni.
Ulac tiɣmert ur nessefqed ara, hatan tura nettwaṭṭef.
Ad sen-nhudd tamuɣli-nni tahuskayt i sɛan ɣef umaḍal.
Ad as-iruḥ deg tazwara beqqu, sakkin tazmert i usnulfu.
Imir-a, neẓra irkelli belli anagar tamettant i aɣ-yettganin.
Ɣur-s nettat, anagar yiwet n tidet i yellan, ulac amkan i tayeḍ.
Asmi ara yesdukkel ayen yelhan d wayen n diri deg yiwet n tcekkart.
Iztikiyen, nitni, ttwasefḍen d asfaḍ seg umezruy deg kra n wayyuren.
Kulci yemtawa ɣef yiqerra-nsen iwakken ad fken amedya ɣef tmettant n tɣermiwin.
Tamaneɣt n Yiztikiyen, Miksiku, tella d aɣrem amexlul n wid yettganin tamettant.
Deg tmurt-iw, yella yiwen n yinzi i d-yeqqaren, win yewwi wasif, yeckunṭud ula deg yisennanen.
Zedɣen deg umtiweg-nniḍen, urǧin i asen-d-truḥ tikti belli akkin i yillel, llan yimdanen-nniḍen.
Tettwali deg tmenɣiwt n wayeḍ d anemgal-is : wayeḍ ɣur-s, d win ur nezmir ad neqbel, d abeɛɛuq.
La aɣ-qqaren, urar-a, d aqbur : yebda seg wasmi llan yimdanen, rnu ttnaɣen gar-asen seg zik n zik.
Yessefk fell-aɣ ad nebges, ad nḥareb ɣef umeɣrad iwakken ad t-nessemneɛ ur iɣelli ara ddaw n yizenẓaren ibelkamen.
Mi ara d-yenqer kan yiṭij, ẓran yakan akud i asen-yettunefken yettwaḥseb s cceḥḥa, ɣef waya, ikeccem-iten uqlileḥ.
Fiḥel ma nessečča-asen tateffaḥt i nessebleɛ nekni yiwen n wass deg wussan n Rebbi : anagar tuɛrin-nsen ara sen-d-tmel.
Tamuɣli-a teččur d nniya, maca tgellu-d s tmettant.
Tanezzut n waklan tessenzef Tafriqt, maca ur tessaweḍ ara ad tessenger Iberkanen irkelli.
Awal ameqqran iqeṭṭu-d, awal amecṭuḥ iqeṭṭu-d.
Ṭebbeg sya!
